    "causal_summary": "Standalone Product Owner skill for Barter backlog work and source-safe product or engineering documentation. Routes every request into one of five intents (Task, Bug, Doc, Story, Interactive) through an exact-command, artifact-framing, then semantic-confidence detection sequence, applies the DEPTH thinking system at the detected energy level, and exports a verified markdown artifact before offering ClickUp delivery. It matters because it is the one discoverable identity for Barter Product Owner artifact creation and refinement, keeping backlog outcomes and documentation source-status distinct and export-verified.",
